text:
Ah, welcome back
…How did it go?

Yep… Mom was real happy.
She said she's gonna cheer for our debut live!
Our debut live is comin' up soon~…

Hehe… You know,
if it weren't for you, I wouldn't have made it this far.

Well, it's because Kogane worked hard
It's Kogane's strength

That's not it… You findin' me
and watchin' over me, it's all thanks to you, Producer.

This much is an undeniable fact!
Come on, just admit it~!

O-Okay, okay…!
Yeah, I'm happy I could be of help to you, too

With you as our producer,
I feel like we can go anywhere!

We'll always, always…
be an unbeatable team!
